-al-afiyah","tag-whims-al-hawa","tag-worldly-life-dunya"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Tu","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":11356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/15\/lesser-greater-jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":26504,"position":0},"title":"Ibrahim on Jihad: Greater Jihad is struggle to purify the heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Ibrahim ibn Abi 'Alqamah, may Allah have mercy on him, said to his people when they returned from a military expedition, \u201cYou have come from the lesser jihad, but you have not performed the greater jihad.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat is the greater jihad?\u201d Ibrahim said, \u201cIt is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20232,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/27\/hasan-jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":26504,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Jihad: Best jihad is against your soul, desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: It was said to Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cO Abu Sa\u2019id, which jihad is best?\u201d Hasan said, \u201cYour jihad against your desires.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-Muh\u0323ibbi\u0304n 1\/478 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0635\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u064